---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageSection from "../components/PageSection.astro";
import ContentSection from "../components/ContentSection.astro";
---
<Layout
        title="About | Techit Thawiang"
        description="Learn more about me—my name, age, interests, history, and everything that defines who I am."
        navTitle="Know more,<br/>about me."
        ogTitle="About Me, Techit Thawiang"
        ogDescription="Let's get to know more about me!"
        ogUrl="https://techit.win/about"
>
    <PageSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <p >Hi, My name is Techit Thawiang. A <span class="text-highlight">fifteen</span> years old kid with a passion on many thing, especially coding. You can call me Sumo, that&apos;s my nickname.</p>
        </ContentSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <p >This is what I look like.</p>
            <img class="this-is-me" alt="Techit in 2023" src="https://files.techit.win/images/custom/PFP/90890uf345289ju02f345j289f345ju89023f452ju38940f52345f8ju90.png"/>
            <p style="font-size:13px;">Me at school doing English "Spelling Bee competition"</p>
        </ContentSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <p >When I'm not working on my coding projects, I’m busy exploring other interests like gaming, reading about tech innovations, and learning new ways to push myself beyond my limits. I believe every mistake is a lesson, and I love improving from each one.</p>
        </ContentSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <p >One day, I hope to use my coding skills to build something big—maybe create tools or apps that others find helpful and enjoyable.</p>
        </ContentSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <p >For now, I’m just a teen who loves to learn and explore new possibilities in tech.</p>
        </ContentSection>
    </PageSection>
    <PageSection display="grid" className="main-child-grid-2-col">
        <ContentSection class="cell">
            <p >About this Website</p>
            <p>
                This website is built with Astro, which I didn't really wanted to.<br/>
                Using web frameworks can be tricky and hard to learn, but yeah it can do what I want as I'm super lazy.<br/><br/>
                If you’d like to create your own simple personal page, check it out at <a class="link" href="https://github.com/techitwinner/web">github.com/techitwinner/web</a>.<br/>
                It’s completely free and open-source, licensed under the MIT license.
            </p>
        </ContentSection>
        <ContentSection class="cell">
            <p >Where is the Thai language?</p>
            <p>
                Although it was once available, I prefer to keep things simple.<br/><br/>
                Implementing internationalization (i18n) can be challenging without JavaScript and external tools,<br/>so reintroducing Thai seems unnecessary.
            </p>
        </ContentSection>
    </PageSection>
    <PageSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <p >Love you all,<br/>Thanks for reading.</p>
        </ContentSection>
    </PageSection>
</Layout>